24
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,565
<i>Hei, Jiyong.</i>

25
00:02:42,315 --> 00:02:44,359
Choi Miryeo putus kontak
beberapa hari ini.

26
00:02:44,776 --> 00:02:46,153
<i>Sepertinya dia diculik.</i>

27
00:02:47,863 --> 00:02:49,364
