Ya, dan mungkin masih ada lagi.

218
00:24:52,604 --> 00:24:55,107
- Tangkap dia!
- Tangkap bajingan itu!

219
00:24:55,774 --> 00:24:57,442
- Hei!
- Bajingan!

220
00:25:04,324 --> 00:25:05,826
- Minggir!
- Hei, minggir.

221
00:25:07,077 --> 00:25:10,539
